    "faq": {
        "title": "Common",
        "inquiries": "Inquiries",
        "description": "Everything you need to know about the SaaSFoodTech platform.",
        "q1": "How does delivery tracking work?",
        "a1": "Our engine uses highly optimized spatial queries (MySQL ST_Distance_Sphere) to retrieve food orders within a 50km radius of your restaurant location. We also provide a trigonometric fallback for local development on SQLite.",
        "q2": "Is the AI menu enhancement mandatory?",
        "a2": "Not at all. Restaurants can choose to 'Enhance' their rough descriptions via our integrated AI service, but original text is preserved if the service is bypassed or fails.",
        "q3": "Can I manage multiple staff accounts?",
        "a3": "Yes. Our Advanced RBAC system supports 'Restaurant Admin' roles that can manage permissions for multiple 'Restaurant Staff' accounts within the same organization.",
        "q4": "How is session security handled?",
        "a4": "We prioritize security over convenience by using httpOnly, secure, SameSite=Lax cookies for session management. This effectively mitigates common XSS and CSRF attack vectors."
    },
